Package com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.dto

com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppCategoryDto
    DTO containing a category name and abbreviation identifier.
    AppDto
    DTO containing the application identifier.
    AppEventDto
    DTO for exchanging application data via events.
    AppIdEventDto
    DTO for exchanging the application id via events.
    AppTaxonomyDto
    DTO containing the application version taxonomy classes.
    AppVersionCollectionDto
    DTO containing application version informations.
    AppVersionDto
    DTO containing the application version information.
    AppVersionTaxonomyClassEventDto
    DTO for exchanging application version taxonomy class mappings via events.
    CategoryDto
    DTO containing category information.
    LayerDto
    DTO containing taxonomy layer information.
    TaxonomyAppsDto
    DTO containing the application version identifiers.
    TaxonomyClassDto
    DTO containing the taxonomy class informations.
    TaxonomyClassPostDto
    DTO containing the category ids of a new taxonomy class.
    TaxonomyDto
    DTO containing the taxonomy informations.
    TaxonomyInfoDto
    DTO containing detailed category information.
